From 8d7d59d6ff401ac23b5e2ccebc66fc90db53c612 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: "Ryan X. Charles" <ryan@ryanxcharles.com>
Date: Wed, 11 Feb 2026 06:18:43 -0600
Subject: [PATCH] Add Two Profiles app with throttle bypass
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

Two contexts, one window, side by side—
Last time they ran at two fps (we cried).
But now with three layers unthrottled and free,
disable_hidden, no scheduler, compositor spree,
Both profiles spin at full stride.

Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>
